"With the beer closing its taste, a final glimpse of mint cooling, herbal bitterness and citrus acidity plays into a playful taste and lively feel. Falling short of classic Belgian versions, Warped Wing's Belgian Style Cream Ale finds sure favor with those seeking more than the bland industrial brewer's offering that scour the market."
